boot.repair@gmail.com or to your favorite support forum.
Locked-NVram detected. Please do not forget to make your UEFI firmware boot on the Ubuntu 24.04.3 LTS entry (nvme0n1p1/efi/ubuntu/grubx64.efi file) !


